title: New Creator: George Clanton
body:
New Creator: George Clanton (100% Electronica music label)

Social Handle: https://twitter.com/MirrorKissesVA, https://twitter.com/100pelectronica

Info:  George Clanton is an American electronic musician and singer-songwriter known for being one of the pioneers in the vaporwave music scene.  He established an independent record label 100% Electronica.  He does VR streams on Twitch, manages other electronic musicians (and their merch) on his label, creates music, hosts events, and more.  He has been deep in the crypto space for ~6 years and is interested in pushing the limit on what is possible with social tokens.

Targeted Use Case:  George is interested in integrating his Creator Coin into his merch operations as well as dono alerts on Twitch via Stream Labs.  He's also interested in using Creator Coin as a way to pay artists under his label and others in his community.  

Community Treasury Grant Tier: $2,000

A "Yes" vote would approve George Clanton as a creator, and provide a $2,000 grant.

A "No" vote would reject George Clanton.
